videos.description: Ty Jerome makes the steal and pushes in transition as Jack Salt slams home the rebound.
videos.headline: Salt finishes UVA break with putback slam

videos.description: Kyle Guy collides into a screen and needs assistance to the locker room after suffering an apparent knee injury.
videos.headline: UVA's Guy heads to locker room with apparent knee injury

videos.description: Virginia swings the ball to Isaiah Wilkins in the post and he delivers a beautiful pass to De'Andre Hunter for the hoop and harm.
videos.headline: Ball movement frees Hunter for UVA bucket

videos.description: Up 40-39, Matt Farrell comes off a pick and drains the deep triple to increase the Fighting Irish's lead.
videos.headline: Farrell rips deep 3 to pad ND's lead

videos.description: The Cavaliers refuse to let the Fighting Irish get a bucket in the paint, rejecting several shots in a row to eventually earn the ball back.
videos.headline: Virginia protects lead with tenacious defense in paint

videos.description: Bonzie Colson gets the ball at the top of the key but can't get a clear shot off due to the Cavaliers' suffocating defense.
videos.headline: Virginia holds lead with lock-down defense
